				'Requests' Library
⦁	This is a comprehensive guide on how to get the 'requests' library in python.
⦁	This library is essential for most programs.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

				Prerequisites
⦁	Python:
		- To install 'requests' first you need to install python.
		- The official release of python can be found at python.org
⦁	PIP with python:
		- Make sure to tick PIP when installing python [Common Error]

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
					Installing 'Requests'


⦁	 If not installed install PowerShell from https://aka.ms/PSWindows
⦁	RUN:
				pip install requests

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
